<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTPA6">
<l>entai tantaitan taitantaitam mūttappaṉ ēḻpaṭi kāltoṭaṅki</l>
<l>vantu vaḻivaḻi yāṭceykiṉ ṟōntiru vōṇat tiruviḻavi</l>
<l>lantiyam pōti lariyuru vāki yariyai yaḻittavaṉai</l>
<l>pantaṉai tīrappal lāṇṭupal lāyirat tāṇṭeṉṟu pāṭutumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My grandfather’s father’s father’s father’s father for seven generations engaged in [service of the Lord],</l>
<l rend="indent">come, we are servants from generation to generation.</l>
<l>For the purpose of vanquishing [our] bondage we sing “many years, many thousands of years”</l>
<l>to he who, having become the Lion form during the festival of tiruvōṇa (Śravaṇa) at twilight, destroyed the enemy.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
